6w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Fever-Ray-Performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Fever-Ray-Performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Simple Things 音乐节公布了 2023 年的阵容，标志着其在中断四年后回归。</p><p>布里斯托尔音乐节的回归将庆祝其十周年。该音乐节将于 2 月 23 日至 29 日期间举行，届时将有众多艺术家参加，如<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/honeyglaze">Honeyglaze</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gilla-band">Gilla Band</a> 、DITZ、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gazelle-twin">Gazelle Twin</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/warmduscher">Warmduscher</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/miso-extra">Miso Extra</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/keg">KEG</a> 、Spectres、Viji 等。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fever-ray">Fever Ray</a>定于 2024 年 2 月 29 日星期四结束音乐节。</p><p> Simple Things 有史以来第一次将在首日之外举办为期一周的系列活动，以纪念其周年纪念日。该节目将于 2 月 24 日在布里斯托尔灯塔 (Bristol Beacon)、Strange Brew、Rough Trade 和 SWX 等不同场地举行一整天的音乐活动。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CxpqKVSMgxC/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50